Module com.example.gui_programming
Package banking_gui

Class TransactionManagerController

java.lang.Object
banking_gui.TransactionManagerController
public class TransactionManagerController extends Object
Manages user transactions by processing input. Supports transactions such as opening accounts, closing accounts, depositing money, withdrawing money, and printing account details.
Author:
Altay Ozkan, Jeffery Sypytkowski
